GrailsPluginInfo
class PluginInfo
extends groovy.lang.GroovyObjectSupport

Used mainly by the build system that encapsulates access to information about the underlying plugin by delegating to the methods in GrailsPluginUtils.

Authors:
Graeme Rocher
Since:
1.1
